            <details>
                <summary class="sum2">
            Choosing Classes
                </summary>
            <p>
            If you have many data values, you can choose classes. Principles:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li> Use between 5 and 15 classes.
                <li> Keep each class of the same width.
                <li> Do not leave out any class, even if its count zero.
                <li> Make sure that the classes cover all the data.
                <li> Do not overlap the classes.
            </ul>
            </details>


